enb_long_title: Tenth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
sentences: Implementation of Protocol Article 2.3: Chair Benrageb urged Parties to move forward on this issue.
SAUDI ARABIA expressed disappointment about the lack of progress on Article 2.3 since COP-8.
The EU, CANADA and JAPAN stated that Article 2.3 is sufficiently reflected in decision 5/CP.7.
Chair Benrageb will consult informally on the issue.
